      "comment": "\u0060(object,json)\u0060 \u2192 \u0060(item,json)\u0060: a json value narrows to dict so \u0060%x.field%\u0060\nnavigates it at runtime. There is no enduring PLang \u0060object\u0060 type \u2014 item is both\nthe apex and the un-narrowed type. (The \u0060is item\u0060/\u0060is dict\u0060 apex contract is\npinned in C# ItemApexTests; this goal proves the end-to-end narrow \u002B navigation.)",
